@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_agofha(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v0
    v0 = (wp.cos(0.42) / (wp.abs(v1 + 0.16) / wp.sin(v2 + 0.43)))
    v0 = 0.66
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.abs(tmp + 0.19) + (tmp + 0.48 * v0 + 0.14)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(v2) + ((v1 + 0.25 * v0 + 0.99) * (v1 + 0.15 / v2 + 0.37)))
    v1 = (v1 - wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.31)))
    v0 = 0.51
    data[tid] = v0
